We're going to have

00:10:06.300 --> 00:10:09.100
this back attached
to the lens of the camera,

00:10:09.100 --> 00:10:11.660
and not just through the foam,

00:10:11.660 --> 00:10:13.800
we're going to be using
our craft foam as a collar

00:10:13.800 --> 00:10:14.852
that fits around the lens,

00:10:14.852 --> 00:10:15.599
because that way,

00:10:15.599 --> 00:10:17.400
it won't just be one ring
around the lens,

00:10:17.400 --> 00:10:19.240
but actually a bit
