is slightly doubled,

00:13:03.605 --> 00:13:06.200
its like there's a shadow
behind the letters,

00:13:06.200 --> 00:13:09.300
and that's because
our acrylic has two sides

00:13:09.300 --> 00:13:10.300
that are reflecting.

00:13:10.300 --> 00:13:11.917
It's not a very
thick sheet of plastic,

00:13:11.917 --> 00:13:14.439
but the letters are reflecting
off of one side of the acrylic,

00:13:14.439 --> 00:13:16.290
