off of the back

00:13:16.290 --> 00:13:17.700
of the same side of the acrylic.

00:13:17.700 --> 00:13:20.040
So you do get
a slight ghosting effect.

00:13:20.040 --> 00:13:22.100
If you're using a
professional-grade teleprompter,

00:13:22.100 --> 00:13:23.815
