reflective coating applied

00:13:30.500 --> 00:13:32.264
to it in just the right spots,

00:13:32.264 --> 00:13:34.500
in just the right amounts
so that it reflects

00:13:34.500 --> 00:13:35.500
the words nicely,

00:13:35.500 --> 00:13:37.058
but you can still
see through it,

00:13:37.058 --> 00:13:39.300
